{"tid":1115097,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"20歲自閉男住安養院　洗澡中被男院友性侵","createTime":"2019-04-19T02:44:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-19T02:56:35.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0f7d8b52a2e7edf5ffe3990daebf1c40567200a4","tid":1115097,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T02:44:57.000Z","msg":"澳洲一名20歲自閉症男子，在安養院洗澡時，被另一名住院男子啪啪啪。<br />\n據澳洲《The Age》報導，澳洲女子瑪莉亞(Maria Thomas)指出，2015年4月21日，當時住在安養院20歲的兒子馬修(Matthew Thomas )，被院友給性侵。瑪莉亞說，她一直對兒子的奇怪行為困擾，但是兒子不擅言語，所以無法弄清發生了什麼事情，「馬修不想讓我離開他，他一直抓著我的手，不想讓我們走，他一直說『留下來，留下』」。<br />\n就在瑪莉亞確定馬修士被院友跟性侵後幾個月，瑪莉亞的丈夫在2015年9月因心臟病過世，瑪莉亞表示，「我無法讓丈夫回來，也無法改變馬修發生的事情，我唯一能做的就是為我的家人伸張正義」。2017年，維多利亞州監察院的報告中，指出在性侵案發生前5個月，瑪莉亞跟丈夫就曾向社會服務廳投訴，兒子在安養院遭性侵，而該部門沒有理會投訴，也沒安排受害人或加害者提供其他安置。<br />\n報告中也記載馬修被院友性侵的細節，但因為考慮到兩個人的殘疾情況，公部門沒有提出起訴。維多利亞州社會服務廳表示，此案目前正在審理中。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190419/640_2dd7ff7b45e1c81ac8bc5d38e99d1d83.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190419%2F640_2dd7ff7b45e1c81ac8bc5d38e99d1d83.jpg&h=b417eeff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190419/640_1e91b996e6c7f6b8aa4a13100454c150.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190419%2F640_1e91b996e6c7f6b8aa4a13100454c150.jpg&h=6a690470&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nMaria Thomas。翻攝自The Age<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190419/1553000/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190419%2F1553000%2F&d=7%2FYu9khx8AV6Haip52opSVHO27hz5fVRhbnvZL2FK%2Bg%3D&h=03edfd52\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20190419%2F1553000%2F&h=7b25ddb7\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20190419/1553000/</a>"},{"pid":"fae85c1a91b2470bd6e93a8bc25dd06c36bc2456","tid":1115097,"uid":119864,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T02:54:37.000Z","msg":"眼神好唏噓"},{"pid":"1df57e7ae1f56749f4d4b6f0b567edbe90c6d93f","tid":1115097,"uid":2590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T02:56:35.000Z","msg":"sad"}]}